title: Conflicts vs New
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The staging table splits into two sections based on whether each staged tiddler's target title already exists in the wiki:

* ''Conflicts'' -- the target title already exists.  Default action: //skip// (don't touch the existing tiddler).
* ''New'' -- the target title is new.  Default action: //add//.

The split is computed at Convert time and re-evaluated if you reload the Console; it doesn't update live as you edit the wiki between Convert and Apply.

